eNCA Senior Reporter Aviwe Mtila is following this story for us. Courtesy #DStv403 BLOEMFONTEIN - Gupta-linked businessman Iqbal Sharma will spend the weekend behind bars. Sharma and three former Free State Agriculture officials appeared before the Bloemfontein magistrate's court on Thursday morning. READ: Gupta-linked businessman to appear in court They were charged with alleged corruption in a project linked to the Estina Dairy Farm project. One of his co-accused will apply for bail with him, while the other two will apply on Thursday afternoon. * eNCA Senior Reporter Aviwe Mtila is following this story for us.